snippet: Phelps’s next event at the United States long-course national championships is the 100-meter butterfly, but after two years away from the sport, he returns to a more competitive landscape.
abstract: Michael Phelps, after two years away from swimming, has returned to more competitive landscape; after seventh-place finish in 100-meter freestyle at the United States long-course swimming championships, he will face more competitive opposition in 100-meter butterfly.
lead_paragraph: Phelps’s next event at the United States long-course national championships is the 100-meter butterfly, but after two years away from the sport, he returns to a more competitive landscape.

headline.main: Michael Phelps’s Best Event Is Same, but Talent Is Deeper
headline.print_headline: More Talent Awaits Phelps in Butterfly
